s can now target player much lower.\nBUGFIX: Test Mode (settings.ini) obstacle interactions re-enabled.\nBUGFIX: Level Difficulty Rating adjustments.\nCHANGE: Replaced tuturial (HiRes) arena with SciFi arena.\nCHANGE: Tutorial levels (2-5) only require user to repeat once instead of twice.\nCHANGE: Tutorial UI panel is now inside TV.\nCHANGE: Updated SciFi Level 8 and Pirates Level 9, 10, 11 and 12.\nCHANGE: Pirates > ShipWheel now launched with random tilt.\n\nVERSION: 0.40.0.7\nBUGFIX: Platform outer rings color now fades correctly when level starts (instead of black).\nBUGFIX: Select level panels now scroll to the very top when opening.\nBUGFIX: Select campaign level text adjusted to not overlap the lock symbol.\nBUGFIX: Cleaned up lighting in SciFi arena.\nBUGFIX: SciFi DroneFast can now target player much lower.\nBUGFIX: Obstacles should no longer get stuck on opposite side portal.\nCHANGE: No longer show errors to player unless in Test Mode or in Editor.", "created_date": 1722013828, "id": "7249522575149260", "version": "0.40.0.8", "version_code": 596, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7475591059209076"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1721507585, "id": "7216988418402676", "version": "0.40.0.6", "version_code": 592, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "An